0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=b8768123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3022668/riot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Court 出左injunction ，聽日仲入去既，自己睇路，<br />\n林鄭就係想拎&ldquo;<ins>法庭授權警察清機場&rdquo;</ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"0b74b699a2fffe0cfcbec0b57171488c08631e8e","tid":1468181,"uid":182933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a7b0164c175f5da65199911e589cc3e4994b6ff","tid":1468181,"uid":1079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"聽日入去同旅客say個sorry 挽回民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950dd4b290b5faa328a195f64f22e244f3de2d37","tid":1468181,"uid":295455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"771358daeb9d33337f17dfe1d1b1b7fb936aba96","tid":1468181,"uid":1079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Set一段緩衝期 然後再重啟和你飛計劃</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n經過呢2日和你飛其實大家所知嘅最大成成果就係透過打擊經濟同國際形象黎對政府施壓<br />\n<br />\n雖然大家其中一個原意係想向遊客宣傳抗爭嘅事<br />\n但似乎成效唔大 反而收到遊客嘅不滿聲音<br />\n因為始終香港唔係佢地嘅居住地方<br />\n多數遊客都唔會受打動 反而會覺得自己行程受阻而不滿<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家需要作出取捨 既然情感渲染遊客嘅計劃未如理想<br />\n應該將大目標放係打擊經濟同國際形象上面<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而set緩衝期就係一個理想嘅方法</span></span></strong><br />\n文宣可以向外國大力宣傳未來某個日子將會再次有和你飛計劃 比依家本黎係香港嘅旅客可以有時間離開 亦都比計劃來港嘅外國人考慮是否仍堅持訪港<br />\n<br />\n旅客減少來港對經濟影響未必好大 但影響運貨飛機就絕對係唔可以睇少 大家有睇出面嘅post應該就會明白<br />\n<br />\n而且令旅客有個心理準備 都可以減低佢地係香港機場嘅負面感受帶返自己國家嘅機會 唔好睇少人傳人 呢d由當地人親身感受嘅經歷隨時比咁耐以黎嘅外國文宣更有殺傷力<br />\n<br />\n當旅客受呼籲後仍然堅持留港或訪港 咁都無咁重怨氣<br />\n<br />\n長遠可以減少來港遊客 更令未來嘅和你飛行動更少反對聲音<br />\n咁就可以繼續執行主線<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>打擊香港經濟及國際形象黎對政府施壓</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n但大家要有心理準備會更加危險 因為無左旅客嘅掩護<br />\n會令狗更加無後顧地圍捕<br />\n但狗係機場做嘅每一樣拘捕行動 其實都係直接打香港嘅國際形象<br />\n當你能夠忍辱負重 所帶黎嘅收獲絕對唔少<br />\n<br />\n至於重啟日期我建議係八月月底 比多少少時間旅客處理同考慮行程安排 同時要係開學前舉行 確保學生可以到場參加<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:36.000Z","msg":"[幫推]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球道歉運動! </span></strong><br />\n推到去&quot;民間記者會&quot;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Say 句 Sorry, 好易啫 ~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n#團結! Be water! Be humble! 香港人有禮貌!<br />\n#816轉美元!<br />\n#612 721 805 811 812<br />\n#和理非勇武！團結d好無！"},{"pid":"e2e7ed7c9ccd6a98cff7fc6198d690b29339bedc","tid":1468181,"uid":1079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61b7e7e4eb56c3dc3ff60e08c21ad011f5737af","tid":1468181,"uid":1079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e74de51bc30b87bbbc1f30767471c779b75472b","tid":1468181,"uid":1079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" 